  </div>
  <div class="about-text">
    <h2>Our History</h2>
    <p>
      KOI Thé is a popular bubble tea brand that originated in Taiwan as part of
      the 50 Lan chain before rebranding to expand internationally. Known for
      its premium quality teas and unique golden tapioca pearls, KOI Thé offers
      a refined tea experience with a focus on fresh ingredients and
      customizable sweetness and ice levels. The brand has grown globally, with
      locations across Asia, the U.S., and other regions. Its signature drinks,
      such as Golden Bubble Milk Tea, Oolong Milk Tea, and Green Tea Macchiato,
      have helped establish KOI Thé as a go-to destination for bubble tea
      lovers, providing a consistent and high-quality beverage experience
      worldwide.
    </p>
    <a href="#" class="btn">Learn more</a>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Products Section -->
<div class="container" id="products">
  <div class="row">
    <% products.forEach(product => { %>
    <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4 col-sm-6 mb-4">
      <div class="card shadow-lg border-light rounded">
        <img
          src="<%= product.image %>"
          class="card-img-top"
          alt="<%= product.name %>"
        />
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title text-center"><%= product.name %></h5>
          <p class="card-text text-center"><%= product.description %></p>
          <a href="/product/<%= product.id %>" class="btn btn-primary w-100"
            >View Details</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <% }); %>
  </div>
</div>
